background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">\RStudio-Desktop"</span></span></code></pre></div></li>
</ul>
</section>
<section id="optional-clean-r-and-r-packages-1" class="level3">
<h3 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="optional-clean-r-and-r-packages-1"><strong>Optional: Clean R and R Packages</strong></h3>
<ul>
<li><p>If installed with Chocolatey, uninstall R:</p>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb10" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode powershell code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode powershell"><span id="cb10-1">choco uninstall <span class="fu" style="color: #4758AB;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">r</span><span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">.</span><span class="fu" style="color: #4758AB;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">project</span></span></code></pre></div></li>
<li><p>Manually delete any installed R packages:</p>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb11" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode powershell code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode powershell"><span id="cb11-1"><span class="fu" style="color: #4758AB;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">Remove-Item</span> <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>Recurse <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
